CShort is a personal URL Shortener server written in C. It uses libmicrohttpd for basic HTTP Server functions, tdb as the data store and is usually run behind an nginx reverse proxy providing authentication and logging.

URL Structure

GET /      Explanatory page, some basic marketing
POST /link Create short link
GET /<l>   Redirect to long equivalent of <l> if present, 404 if not

It will be released under three clause BSD. And security tested.
